https://flathub.org/

flatpak remotes

flatpak remote-add {give_a_name} https://dl.flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo
ex:
flatpak remote-add repositorio https://dl.flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo
flatpak remote -ls {repositorio}

comandos:
flatpak update
flatpak remove uninstall {app_name}
flatpak install {app_name}
flatpak search vlc

flatpak remote-info flathub {application_name}
Ex:
flatpak remote-info flathub org.videolan.org

flatpak install org.videolan.VLC

flatpak list
flatpak list --app

flatpak run org.videolan.VLC

flatpak --help

